---
title: Toasty Pesto Gnocchi with Green Beans, Sun-Dried Tomatoes, and Parmesan
description: Whether you call them *nyo-kee*, *nyock-ee*, or something else entirely, these potato dumplings are delicious, for sure. How could they not be with a good dollop of pesto to coat them in cheesy, herbaceous flavor? But just to make sure that you’re not left wanting for more Italian-style flair, we’re throwing in sun-dried tomatoes, snappy green beans, and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese.
